window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>He's demanding, and he wants meâ€”in his bed, obeying his every command.</b></p> <p>All my life, I wanted to be loved. Instead, I was ignored.</p> <p>My father gave me what I wanted so he could go back to ignoring me. Once I understood that, life became easier.</p> <p>When he arranged to marry me off to the son of his biggest ally, I didn't mind.</p> <p>Marco was the older brother of my best friend, and honestly, he made me burn.</p> <p>I wanted to belong to him. I wanted in his life, in his bed, and definitely in his heart.</p> <p>It didn't quite work out that way.</p> <p>So, I left.</p> <p>Then, one really bad decision lands me in hot water.</p> <p>Marco steps in.</p> <p>He thinks he's a monster.</p> <p>He's wrong. He's my destiny.</p>"; 
